word_mean_info__list.difference: 一般指四壁没有完全封闭，供牲畜用或储藏东西、停放车辆等的简易棚屋。
多指建造粗糙的简陋小木屋，也指旅客或船员住的船舱。现在也指节假日游游者的简便住房。
多指供居住或遮避风雨的简易小屋。
指穷苦人住的乡间小茅屋。现在也指雅致的小住宅，在美国可指别墅。

bilingual.source: We bought a cottage by the sea.
bilingual.target: 我们买了一间海边的小屋。

bilingual.source: Every day she came to my cottage.
bilingual.target: 每天她都会来我的小屋。

bilingual.source: She left the house and dashed to Grandmama's cottage.
bilingual.target: 她离开了房子，冲向奶奶的小屋。

bilingual.source: We rented a cottage by the lake.
bilingual.target: 我们在湖边租了一间小屋。

bilingual.source: This cottage is perfect for a vacation.
bilingual.target: 这间小屋非常适合度假。
这间小屋有一个用茅草覆盖的屋顶。

bilingual.source: He dwelt in a small cottage by the sea.
bilingual.target: 他居住在海边的一间小屋里。

bilingual.source: He dwells in a small cottage by the lake.
bilingual.target: 他居住在湖边的一间小屋里。

bilingual.source: They lived in a small cottage by the sea.
bilingual.target: 他们在海边的一间小屋里居住。

yingyinNormal.en: The late Emperor was not ashamed to visit my cottage and seek my advice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先帝不以臣卑鄙，猥自枉屈，三顾臣于草庐之中，咨臣以当世之事，

yingyinNormal.en: I had no idea this one was here. The cottage must've been built on top of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不记得以前有这个，这个房间肯定是后来建的。

yingyinNormal.en: Worked very well for a few years. I bought a nice cottage in Cornwall on the back of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有几年非常顺利。我在康沃尔给自己买了一间很棒的农舍。

yingyinNormal.en: Not quite, but it's better. Yes. And you've moved back into the cottage. I have, My Lady.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还没完全解决，但是好多了。那你搬回农舍了吧。是的，小姐。

yingyinNormal.en: How do you know? Well, on your salary, it would have to be modest, and you spent all the money on that cottage, didn't you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么知道？凭你的工资，你不能过得太阔绰，而且你把钱都花在那间农舍上了吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs Cobb is going to live with her daughter in Oswaldkirk so Mary's going to give the cottage to the Carsons. Excellent news.
yingyinNormal.zh: 柯布太太要去跟女儿一起住在奥斯沃德科克，这样的话玛丽会把农舍赠给卡森夫妇。好极了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a small house, usually in the countryside

examination_example.sentence: The entire ground floor of our <highlight>cottage</highlight> was submerged in water, and five of us have been living in a caravan ever since.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们小屋的整个底层都被水淹没了，从那以后，我们五个人就一直住在一个大篷车里。

examination_example.sentence: The ground floor of their <highlight>cottage</highlight> was flooded.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们小屋的一楼被水淹了。

examination_example.sentence: The roof of their <highlight>cottage</highlight> collapsed in the flood.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们的小屋的屋顶在洪水中倒塌了。
